<D>__{don't help me.}
<C>__{bloom}
<D>__{he's a liar and a cheat and a scoundrel. he's taken money from little old ladies. he's talked people into doing things they never would have dreamed of. especially me. but who has he really hurt?}
<C>__{bloom }
<D>__{who are the victims? not me, i had the most exciting adventure of my life. and what about the little old ladies? what would their lives have been without max bialystock? he made them feel wanted and young and attractive again.}
<C>__{little old ladies}
